---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Research · Deep Pearl"
  description="The lines of work Deep Pearl is studying and building."
>
  <article class="thread-page wrap">
    <a class="back" href="/">
      <span aria-hidden="true">&larr;</span>
      <span>Deep Pearl</span>
    </a>

    <h1>Research</h1>
    <p class="lede">The lines of work Deep Pearl is studying and building.</p>

    <div class="research-groups">
      <section class="research-group" aria-labelledby="g-rep">
        <h2 id="g-rep">Representation and learning</h2>
        <ul class="studying-list">
          <li>representation learning</li>
          <li>self supervised learning</li>
          <li>JEPA style predictive learning</li>
          <li>non backprop and brain inspired learning</li>
          <li>interpretability</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section class="research-group" aria-labelledby="g-sym">
        <h2 id="g-sym">Reasoning and symbol</h2>
        <ul class="studying-list">
          <li>systematic task solving</li>
          <li>symbolic reasoning</li>
          <li>neural symbolic systems</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section class="research-group" aria-labelledby="g-scale">
        <h2 id="g-scale">Scaling and routing</h2>
        <ul class="studying-list">
          <li>mixture of experts</li>
          <li>dynamic routing</li>
          <li>sparsity</li>
          <li>adaptive computation</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section class="research-group" aria-labelledby="g-edge">
        <h2 id="g-edge">Edge and embodiment</h2>
        <ul class="studying-list">
          <li>edge deployment</li>
          <li>robotic integration</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>

    <p class="applied-line">Applied across Multivac, Multivac Physics, ALEX-1, and EMOTE4D.</p>

    <aside class="influences">
      <p class="label">Influences</p>
      <p>World model and edge AI research by the author of <a href="https://github.com/yuedajiong" rel="noopener">github.com/yuedajiong</a>.</p>
    </aside>
  </article>
</Layout>
